item.title: Are there any way?
item.dc:creator: @davidude36 Brolapse
item.description:
@davidude36 wrote:

[quote=“Frell, post:4, topic:147652”][quote author=davidude36 link=topic=202001.msg1790538#msg1790538 date=1191165685]
There are no stat changers, and don’t go looking for them because you will end up getting your password stolen.

The golden rule “If something seems to good to be true, don’t trust it”

There are auto’s and bots… they are about the only runescape cheating left (apart from scamming, which is becoming harder by the day and is also not supported by www.moparisthebest.com)

So no there arent any stat changers or money cheats.
[/quote]scamming has become easier. People put up 2m, suptract to 1m, so the light thing is already blinking, then change 1000k to 10004, and accept.[/quote]
never heard of that! Although i did stop playing a month ago. Scamming will always be in the game…
